{{Unreferenced|date=June 2009}}

'''''Uncommon Threads''''' is a TV craft show on the [[DIY Network]], hosted by [[Allison Whitlock]]. The series focuses on the art of [[needlecraft]]s, including [[appliqué]], [[crochet]], [[embroidery]], [[patchwork]], [[quilting]] and [[rug making]]. The host is joined on each show by a different needle arts group, club, or designer from around the United States. Viewers get to know the guests as they share their ideas, specialties, techniques and creations.

